{"tid":1996671,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"根據大波華呢件事，有無人覺得逃輝都係玩自爆比蘋果聽??","createTime":"2020-05-01T06:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T06:15:49.000Z","uid":261300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c35430577d7cd2096025e23f96c1725d6d7efe32","tid":1996671,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"大波華岩岩上任就爆左僭建同上市呢件事，結果要死保佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無因D黑材料而逼走佢，之後佢無哂D把柄係人手。佢開開心心跑去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後番黎都係拉佢上北京而無得爆佢大獲，因為已經爆哂出黎，威脅唔到佢，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地都好難而家先番轉頭追究咁耐之前既案</span></strong></span>，而家值得風平浪靜，十足早爆早享受，遲爆唔會平三年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而逃輝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係正5月1呢個吹到有大動作就日子前爆咁</span></strong></span>既，佢地都係要死保逃輝，結果又係安然渡過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好似林平之拆flag法既終極版</span></strong></span>，係最多人保既時候自爆，保完佢事後又好難因為番呢件事而追究，而我地都已經對件事淡左，無咁大攻擊性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">十一哥機會黎</span></strong></span>啦，唔想下半世比人控制，係呢個時間自爆，有人保唔怕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}